<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>223</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mangthai ding hukdam in, thi ding enkawl in,
 Gitloh, thihna apat ladawk kinin;
 Migilo hehpih in, a puk phawngding in,
 Hukdam ding a hat, Isu thu hilh un.

[V2]
 Mangthai ding hukdawk un, thiding enkawl un;
 Isu hehpihna chun hukdam ina.

[V3]
 2. Amah musit mahleu, Ama'n A ngak zing,
 Kisik a lungheite pawm di'n A ngak;
 Gunchuh takin chiel in, zaidam in them in,
 A ginchak phawt uchun ngaidam ina.

[V4]
 3. Lunggil ngaihtuohna pha thempa'n a suksiet,
 Amah lungsietna'n a hun siempha thei;
 Lungsiet khuta khawih in, nunnem nan phawngin,
 Ana siesa chuh hung pha kit ina.

[V5]
 4. Mangthai ding hukdawk un, I sep ding ahi,
 Nasep hatna ding Lalpa'n hun piena;
 Lamneu hawh kit dingin gunchuh in them un,
 Vakvaite Hukdampa thih thu hilh un.</lyrics>
<title>RESCUE THE PERISHING</title>
</song>